name: Verify: 70% of the returned clips per search term exist in data set | vespa | discussion between husband and wife - Compare to dev
fullName: Verify: 70% of the returned clips per search term exist in data set | vespa | discussion between husband and wife - Compare to dev
descriptionHtml:
We will use the failed cURL from the test and point it to dev. We will then compare the results from dev and dyn test envs.
  If the results are the same, it means that the test is also failing on dev and it is not a regression and might be data issue.
  If the results are different, it means that the test is failing on dyn test env and it is a regression.
